sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner
    participant Frontend
    participant API as Symfony API
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Owner->>Frontend: Open channel members modal
    Frontend->>API: GET /api/workspaces/{workspaceId}/channels/{channelId}/members
    API->>API: Validate JWT and channel administration rights
    API->>DB: Load channel members
    DB-->>API: Member list
    API-->>Frontend: 200 OK + members
    Frontend-->>Owner: Display channel members modal
